Insider Activity


Individual




John J. Suydam



Mr. John J. Suydam is Chief Legal Officer at Apollo Global Management LLC. He is on the Board of Directors at Environmental Solutions Worldwide, Inc., Big Apple Circus, The Legal Action Center and New York University School of Law. Mr. Suydam was previously employed as Chief Legal Officer & Vice President by Apollo Investment Corp., Partner by Graves & O'Melveny, Chief Compliance Officer & Vice President by Apollo Capital Management LP (Investment Management), and Chairman by O'Sullivan LLP. He also served on the board at Quality Distribution, Inc. He received his undergraduate degree from State University of New York at Albany and a graduate degree from New York University School of Law.



