Individual




John J. Suydam



Mr. John J. Suydam is Chief Legal & Compliance Officer at Apollo Global Management LLC. He is on the Board of Directors at Environmental Solutions Worldwide, Inc., Big Apple Circus, New York University School of Law, and The Legal Action Center.
Mr. Suydam was previously employed as Chief Legal Officer & Vice President by Apollo Investment Corp., Partner by Graves & O'Melveny, Chairman by O'Sullivan LLP, and Chief Compliance Officer & Vice President by Apollo Capital Management LP. He also served on the board at Quality Distribution, Inc.
He received his undergraduate degree from the State University of New York at Albany and a graduate degree from the New York University School of Law.



